---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ArticleCTA from '../../components/ArticleCTA.astro';
import RelatedServices from '../../components/RelatedServices.astro';

const SITE = 'https://ltsmobilemechanics.com';
const slug = 'emergency-roadside';
const serviceTitle = 'Emergency Roadside';

const schemaData = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  "name": `Mobile ${serviceTitle} Service`,
  "description": `Professional mobile ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()} service in Beaverton, Portland, and the greater Portland metro area. We come to you — 24/7.`,
  "provider": {
    "@type": "LocalBusiness",
    "name": "LT's Mobile Mechanics",
    "telephone": "+19715340360",
    "url": SITE,
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "4041 SW Hall Blvd",
      "addressLocality": "Beaverton",
      "addressRegion": "OR",
      "postalCode": "97005",
      "addressCountry": "US"
    }
  },
  "areaServed": [
    "Beaverton, OR","Portland, OR","Hillsboro, OR","Tigard, OR",
    "Lake Oswego, OR","Tualatin, OR","Aloha, OR","Gresham, OR"
  ],
  "url": `${SITE}/services/${slug}/`
};
---

<Layout
  title={`Mobile ${serviceTitle} in Beaverton & Portland, OR | LT's Mobile Mechanics`}
  description={`Mobile ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()} service at your home or work in Beaverton, Portland, and the Portland metro. Professional, honest, and available 24/7. Call (971) 534-0360.`}
  keywords={`mobile ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()} Portland, mobile mechanic ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()}, ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()} Beaverton, ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()} Portland Oregon`}
  canonical={`https://ltsmobilemechanics.com/services/${slug}/`}
  schema={schemaData}
>
  <main>
    <section class="article-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>24/7 Emergency Roadside Service in <em>Beaverton and Portland</em></h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Broken down? Stranded? We're here 24/7. Fast roadside assistance anywhere in the Portland metro area.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container">
      <article class="article-body">
        <div class="article-content fade-up">
          <p>A vehicle breakdown can happen anytime, anywhere. You could be sitting on the side of the freeway at rush hour, stuck in a parking lot in the rain at midnight, or stranded far from home with no idea what to do. That's when you need someone who can help fast. LTs Mobile Mechanics provides 24/7 emergency roadside service throughout Beaverton, Portland, and the surrounding metro area. When you're in trouble, Tristan will be there.</p>

          <h2>What Counts as an Emergency</h2>
          <p>Emergency situations come in all forms. Your car won't start and you're late for work. You got a flat tire on a dark road. Your engine overheated and you need help getting to safety. You ran out of gas. Your battery is dead. Your transmission died on the freeway. Your brakes are failing. Any of these can leave you feeling helpless, but they don't have to. Call LTs Mobile Mechanics and help is on the way.</p>

          <h2>We Get There Fast</h2>
          <p>When you call about an emergency breakdown in Beaverton, Portland, or the surrounding areas, we prioritize your call. Tristan will get to you as quickly as possible. We keep you updated on his location and arrival time so you're not left wondering. Whether your breakdown is at 2 PM on a Tuesday or 2 AM on a Sunday, we treat it with the same urgency and professionalism.</p>

          <h2>What We Can Fix on the Spot</h2>
          <p>Many roadside emergencies can be fixed right where you broke down. Dead battery? We can jump start it. Blown fuse? We've got replacements. Hose or belt issue? We might be able to patch it. Flat tire? We can help get you to a tire shop or repair it. Engine overheating? We can assess the situation and advise on next steps. While some problems require towing, many can be resolved quickly so you can get back on the road.</p>

          <h2>Towing and Safe Alternatives</h2>
          <p>If your vehicle can't be fixed on the side of the road, we'll help coordinate towing or transport you somewhere safe. We have relationships with local tow companies and can arrange safe transport to a repair shop or your home. If you need just a ride to get somewhere while your vehicle is being fixed, we can help with that too. Our goal is to get you out of the emergency situation safely.</p>

          <h2>Available Always, Everywhere</h2>
          <p>Here's what makes LTs Mobile Mechanics different for roadside emergencies: we're always available. We don't close at 5 PM. We don't take weekends off. We don't ask you to wait until Monday. When your car breaks down, call us. Tristan will come help you get the problem sorted, whether it's a quick fix or a bigger issue. Open 24/7, 7 days a week throughout Beaverton, Portland, and the entire Portland metro area.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <ArticleCTA
      heading={`Ready for ${serviceTitle}?`}
      subheading={`Call LT's Mobile Mechanics. We come to you in Beaverton, Portland, and throughout the Portland metro — 24/7.`}
    />

    <RelatedServices exclude={slug} />
  </main>
</Layout>
